WEBVTT

00:11.750 --> 00:14.709
♪

00:23.417 --> 00:26.500
[ Young Man ]
SHE WAS THE FIRST GIRL
TO SEE ME NAKED.

00:26.583 --> 00:28.291
GRANTED WE WERE
7 YEARS OLD AT THE TIME,

00:28.375 --> 00:31.875
BUT I HAD A FEELING EVEN THEN.

00:31.959 --> 00:34.166
THERE'S REALLY SOMETHING
ABOUT THE FIRST GIRL
YOU PLAY DOCTOR WITH.

00:34.250 --> 00:35.625
MAYBE IT'S COSMIC OR SOMETHING,

00:35.709 --> 00:38.333
OR PERHAPS IT'S JUST THAT
SHE'S SEEN YOUR PACKAGE

00:38.417 --> 00:40.333
AND DIDN'T RUN AWAY SCREAMING.

00:40.417 --> 00:43.917
WHATEVER IT WAS, ALLISON AND I
WERE MADE FOR EACH OTHER,

00:44.000 --> 00:45.083
A PERFECT FIT.

00:45.166 --> 00:47.208
SO WHEN HER FAMILY MOVED AWAY,

00:47.291 --> 00:52.500
I-- I KNEW THAT SOMEDAY,
SOMEHOW, FATE WOULD BRING US
BACK TOGETHER.

00:54.291 --> 00:55.208
♪ HAPPINESS ♪

00:55.291 --> 00:57.917
[ Allison ]
BERKE.

00:58.000 --> 01:02.208
♪ HAPPINESS ♪
♪ [ Stops ]
BERKE LANDERS.

01:02.291 --> 01:04.250
IT'S ME, ALLISON.

01:04.333 --> 01:06.250
ALLISON MCALLISTER?

01:06.333 --> 01:07.500
♪ [ Resumes ]

01:09.500 --> 01:12.542
OF ALL THE LUNCHROOMS
IN ALL THE SCHOOLS
IN ALL THE WORLD,

01:12.625 --> 01:15.917
THAT DAY,
SHE WALKED INTO MINE.

01:16.000 --> 01:17.583
IT WAS THE PERFECT ROMANCE.

01:17.667 --> 01:20.709
I WAS DATING THE MOST
BEAUTIFUL GIRL IN SCHOOL.

01:20.792 --> 01:24.250
AND THE COOL PART?
WE STILL PLAYED DOCTOR.

01:24.333 --> 01:26.875
♪ HAPPINESS ♪

01:26.959 --> 01:30.250
FOR THE FIRST TIME IN MY LIFE,
I WAS IN LOVE,

01:30.333 --> 01:32.208
AND I KNEW
IT WOULD LAST FOREVER.

01:34.333 --> 01:36.000
BOY, WAS I A DUMB-ASS.

01:38.792 --> 01:40.500
WE NEED TO TALK.

01:42.542 --> 01:47.291
UM, YOU KNOW,
EVERYTHING IN LIFE,

01:47.375 --> 01:50.417
E-- EVEN THE REALLY GREAT
THINGS,

01:50.500 --> 01:52.875
RUN THEIR COURSE EVENTUALLY.

01:52.959 --> 01:54.208
RIGHT?

01:54.291 --> 01:56.291
TRENDS FADE.

01:56.375 --> 01:59.250
BREAD MOLDS.

01:59.333 --> 02:02.041
PEOPLE DIE.

02:02.125 --> 02:04.041
UH-HUH.

02:04.125 --> 02:05.750
[ Sighs ]

02:05.834 --> 02:08.750
I GUESS--

02:08.834 --> 02:11.959
REMEMBER THE FIRST TIME
WE KISSED?

02:12.041 --> 02:15.291
THE FEELING, THE SPARKS?

02:15.375 --> 02:17.083
YEAH.

02:17.166 --> 02:20.917
WELL, NOW WHEN WE KISS,

02:21.000 --> 02:22.083
THE FEELING,

02:22.166 --> 02:23.333
IT'S--
IT'S KIND OF--

02:25.375 --> 02:27.208
IT'S KIND OF GONE.

02:39.041 --> 02:40.542
OH, AND, BERKE?

02:44.709 --> 02:47.083
I PACKED UP MOST OF YOUR STUFF.

02:48.083 --> 02:49.417
I THOUGHT IT'D BE EASIER.

02:52.291 --> 02:53.625
THANKS.

03:17.458 --> 03:18.834
♪ LOVE ♪

03:18.917 --> 03:22.291
♪ LOVE WILL KEEP US TOGETHER ♪

03:22.375 --> 03:25.625
♪ THINK OF ME BABE WHENEVER ♪

03:25.709 --> 03:29.375
