05:33.542 --> 05:36.709
♪ DAH-DA-DA-DAH ♪

05:36.792 --> 05:39.542
AAAAAAH!

05:47.291 --> 05:50.333
[ Berke ]
MY PARENTS, FRANK AND BEVERLY,
THEY HOST THE, UH,

05:50.417 --> 05:52.792
RELATIONSHIP ADVICE SHOW
LOVE MATTERS,
[ Studio Audience Applauding ]

05:52.875 --> 05:54.500
WHICH SOUNDS PRETTY COOL--

05:54.583 --> 05:56.500
THIS MAXIMIZES THE PLEASURE
FOR BOTH PARTNERS.

05:56.583 --> 05:58.333
EXACTLY, RIGHT, RIGHT, AND, AND

05:58.417 --> 06:01.208
WHILE SIMULTANEOUSLY ALLOWING
FOR FACE-TO-FACE INTIMACY.

06:01.291 --> 06:02.709
[ Frank ]
COOLIO KNOWS WHAT WE'RE TALKING
ABOUT. WHAT DO YOU THINK?

06:02.792 --> 06:05.709
YOU WANNA TAKE HER
FOR A SPIN?
HUH?

06:05.792 --> 06:09.834
WE'LL BE RIGHT BACK.
♪ [ Stinger ]

06:09.917 --> 06:11.166
HERE ARE THE CDS
YOU WANTED, MOM.

06:11.250 --> 06:12.500
OH, THANKS, HONEY.

06:12.583 --> 06:13.625
YOU KNOW,
THE GUESTS GET SO CRANKY

06:13.709 --> 06:15.542
WHEN YOU HAVEN'T HEARD
THEIR MUSIC.

06:15.625 --> 06:18.375
NOW, YOU CAME HOME
SO EARLY LAST NIGHT.

06:18.458 --> 06:19.542
DON'T MAKE IT TOO FLAT.

06:19.625 --> 06:21.542
IS EVERYTHING OK WITH ALLISON?

06:21.625 --> 06:23.917
NO, NOT REALLY. SO MAYBE WE CAN
TALK ABOUT IT--

06:24.000 --> 06:26.542
UH, BERKE, YOU KNOW THE RULE.

06:26.625 --> 06:29.208
WHEN WE'RE NOT
FEELING SUNNY, WE--

06:29.291 --> 06:32.500
I DON'T REALLY WANT
TO TALK ABOUT IT HERE.
I BELIEVE THE WORD IS SHARE.

06:32.583 --> 06:36.166
FRANK, HON, APPARENTLY
BERKE HAS A PROBLEM
WITH ALLISON.

06:36.250 --> 06:39.667
WHAT'S THE STORY, DUDE?
A LITTLE SNAFU IN THE OLD
CHANNELS OF COMMUNICATION?

06:39.750 --> 06:41.542
BOUNDARY ISSUES?
CODEPENDENCY?

06:41.625 --> 06:43.208
NO, IT'S, IT'S NOTHING
LIKE THAT.

06:43.291 --> 06:44.667
[ Floor Manager ]
FIVE MINUTES, PEOPLE.

06:44.750 --> 06:46.291
[ Parents ]
SEX.

06:47.625 --> 06:49.583
SHE DUMPED ME.

06:49.667 --> 06:51.917
DARLING.
[ Studio Audience ]
AWW!

06:52.000 --> 06:55.834
[ Woman In Audience ]
OHH! YOU POOR BABY!

06:55.917 --> 06:58.417
THIS PROBABLY ISN'T
THE BEST PLACE
TO TALK ABOUT THIS.

