OK, OK, OK.

46:22.667 --> 46:23.959
JUST KEEP AN EYE ON HER, MAN.

46:24.041 --> 46:25.458
YOU KNOW, 'CAUSE SOME
OF THOSE THEATER GUYS

46:25.542 --> 46:28.041
THEY HAVE THIS REPUTATION
OF BEING KINDA--

46:28.125 --> 46:30.875
GAY?
SEE, THAT'S WHAT
THEY WANT YOU TO THINK.

46:30.959 --> 46:31.917
[ Berke ]
I'LL KEEP AN EYE ON HER.

